{"tid":363430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴耀廷：符合民主　自決、港獨分歧不大　中國可完全分裂　可以聯邦中國","createTime":"2017-08-17T15:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T16:10:32.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28ba546c4998e7e29c44b2ef3853be33b66295e4","tid":363430,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170812/57072569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170812%2F57072569&d=wf1j%2FBAVpNFcDbTK2ztEX9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b5ddcd9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170812%2F57072569&h=68ceab85\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170812/57072569</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170812/large/1502518740_23fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170812%2Flarge%2F1502518740_23fb.jpg&h=82d9bd91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港大法律系副教授戴耀廷指，當日中共8.31決定是分界線，中共可以給香港的自治、民主，原來並不是港人一直所想的，充其量是「威權式」的。另外中共行的是長久政策，不能抱著中共內有不同派系的幻想。他又預料打壓陸續有來下，認為港人不能再相信《基本法》框架，要實現自主，《基本法》不能做到，故要準備長期抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n他又指中國內的變化是會發生，但不知道何時，有機會是中共自我修正，作政治改革，但可能性低；亦可能是中國崩潰、碎片化。他指將問題想得遠一些時，若未來是中國四分五裂或聯邦中國，香港現在談的港獨、自決就分歧不大。共通都是想主權在民，追求港人可以自主地管理。"},{"pid":"ab4e345f98a4c8dc928c22d7e10d488c546d5990","tid":363430,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"學陳雲？"},{"pid":"1804e6de1049d1ac9782655d59a60432a32a94be","tid":363430,"uid":36058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"其實係本土同港獨派太心急，唔韜光養晦，等待時機。暫時扮住乏民或左膠或大中華膠先，時機成熟先露真章。"},{"pid":"75e5cca34cca16f1e1056b93cd0113c065b9d4a7","tid":363430,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:10:32.000Z","msg":"國師mode"}]}